<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ880309-0128 </DOCNO><HL> Surplus of Workers in China </HL><SO> </SO><CO> FREST </CO><DATELINE> BEIJING  </DATELINE><TEXT>   China has 20 million surplus workers, although there are substantial shortages in jobs requiring heavy labor, the official China Daily said.    The English-language newspaper said the surplus in the nation's labor force of 132 million people is costing the state billions of yuan and is creating a heavy burden on enterprises. </TEXT></DOC>